            Suppose the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">management</ENAMEX> of a
large <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">corporation</ENAMEX> (call it <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Texaco</ENAMEX>) discriminates against <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">blacks</ENAMEX> in hiring and
promotion. Who are the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">victims</ENAMEX> of that discrimination? The most obvious
